reviewText: good movie I am a ruth roman fan thank you

Johnson plays a fairly convincing drunk.  Relative of yours?  Just like one of mine!
Too real to be that entertaining sometimes.  Shows life back then, with alcohol parties.
Racial discrimination is in there too.  Sandy Descher was my favorite lady when I was her age, and she gets a couple of lines here.
Probably this one should be listed as a One Timer.
It's a potboiler as i knew it would be. But a good one.
